        WHERE_WILL_YOU_GO_KINETIC_UNITS_NOWHERE_THANKS                         = 12744,  -- Where will you go? (Kinetic Units: #) Nowhere, thanks. I'd rather read an explanation. Ru'Lude Gardens. (# unit[/s]) Selbina. (# unit[/s]) Mhaura. (# unit[/s]) Rabao. (# unit[/s]) Norg. (# unit[/s]) West Ronfaure. (# unit[/s]) North Gustaberg. (# unit[/s]) West Sarutabaruta. (# unit[/s]) La Theine Plateau. (# unit[/s]) Konschtat Highlands. (# unit[/s]) Tahrongi Canyon. (# unit[/s]) Jugner Forest. (# unit[/s]) Pashhow Marshlands. (# unit[/s]) Meriphataud Mountains. (# unit[/s]) Attohwa Chasm. (# unit[/s]) Uleguerand Range. (# unit[/s]) Davoi. (# unit[/s]) Beadeaux. (# unit[/s]) Castle Oztroja. (# unit[/s]) Quicksand Caves. (# unit[/s]) Sea Serpent Grotto. (# unit[/s]) Temple of Uggalepih. (# unit[/s]) The Boyahda Tree. (# unit[/s]) Oldton Movalpolos. (# unit[/s]) Riverne - Site #B01. (# unit[/s]) Castle Zvahl Keep. (# unit[/s]) Decline destination confirmation. Accept destination confirmation.
        RECORD_THIS_FOUNT_YES_NO                                               = 12745,  -- Record this fount? Yes. No.
        A_PALPABLE_FORCE_WELLS_UP_SLOWLY_FROM_BENEATH                          = 12746,  -- A palpable force wells up slowly from beneath the surface...
        THIS_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_HAS_ALREADY_BEEN_RECORDED                       = 12747,  -- This geomagnetic fount has already been recorded.
        YOU_HAVE_SUCCESSFULLY_RECORDED_THE_PHENOMENON_NOW_IT                   = 12748,  -- You have successfully recorded the phenomenon. Now it is time to report your findings to Anastase.
        YOUR_RECORDS_SURROUNDING_THE_CURRENT_GEOMAGNETIC_PHENOMENON_HAD        = 12749,  -- Your records surrounding the current geomagnetic phenomenon had been fading, but your use of the % has restored them to normal!
        YOUR_HAS_BEEN_ATTUNED_TO_A_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_2                         = 12750,  -- Your % has been attuned to a geomagnetic fount[ in Selbina/ in Mhaura/ in Rabao/ in Norg]!
        YOUR_HAS_BEEN_ATTUNED_TO_A_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_3                         = 12751,  -- Your % has been attuned to a geomagnetic fount[ in West Ronfaure/ in North Gustaberg/ in West Sarutabaruta/ in La Theine Plateau/ in the Konschtat Highlands/ in Tahrongi Canyon/ in Jugner Forest/ in the Pashhow Marshlands/ in the Meriphataud Mountains/ in Attohwa Chasm/ in Uleguerand Range]!
        YOUR_HAS_BEEN_ATTUNED_TO_A_GEOMAGNETIC_FOUNT_4                         = 12752,  -- Your % has been attuned to a geomagnetic fount[ in Davoi/ in Beadeaux/ in Castle Oztroja/ in the Quicksand Caves/ in Sea Serpent Grotto/ in the Temple of Uggalepih/ in the Boyahda Tree/ in Oldton Movalpolos/ in Riverne - Site #B01/ in Castle Zvahl Keep]!
        YOU_MAY_NOW_TRAVEL_TO_VIA_WAYPOINTS                                    = 12753,  -- You may now travel to [Selbina/Mhaura/Rabao/Norg] via waypoints!
        YOU_MAY_NOW_TRAVEL_TO_VIA_WAYPOINTS_2                                  = 12754,  -- You may now travel to [West Ronfaure/North Gustaberg/West Sarutabaruta/La Theine Plateau/the Konschtat Highlands/Tahrongi Canyon/Jugner Forest/the Pashhow Marshlands/the Meriphataud Mountains/Attohwa Chasm/Uleguerand Range] via waypoints!
        YOU_MAY_NOW_TRAVEL_TO_VIA_WAYPOINTS_3                                  = 12755,  -- You may now travel to [Davoi/Beadeaux/Castle Oztroja/the Quicksand Caves/Sea Serpent Grotto/the Temple of Uggalepih/the Boyahda Tree/Oldton Movalpolos/Riverne - Site #B01/Castle Zvahl Keep] via waypoints!
        HIST_THOU_CANST_SEE_THE_LIGHT_CANST_THOU                               = 12756,  -- Hist! Thou canst see the light, canst thou not? It seems thou hast the talent for which I have been searching.
        THY_LACK_OF_EXPERIENCE_HOWEVER_LEAVETH_A_SINGLE                        = 12757,  -- Thy lack of experience, however, leaveth a single teary trail upon my cheek. Mayhap with more training, thou can attainest further glory.
        EKE_THY_TRAINING_HATH_NOT_BEEN_IN_VAIN                                 = 12758,  -- Eke, thy training hath not been in vain. My only question is that, with thy great powers, dost thou not tire of this corporeal realm?
        HOW_DO_I_KNOW_OF_THY_DEEPEST_DESIRES                                   = 12759,  -- How do I know of thy deepest desires? 'Tis only natural, for the soul doth constantly yearn for greener pastures.
        YET_THE_PASTURE_IT_HATH_BEEN_GIVEN_IS                                  = 12760,  -- Yet the pasture it hath been given is finite. Each soul's lot is to one day meet with its fence. Such wanion!
        YET_WHAT_IF_THERE_WERE_A_METHOD_BY                                     = 12761,  -- Yet what if there were a method by which it could escape its confines and begin life anew?
        SHOULDST_THOU_BE_ENCHANTED_WITH_THESE_ADUMBRATIONS_PROCUREST           = 12762,  -- Shouldst thou be enchanted with these adumbrations, procurest for one of my brethren %, %, or %.
        THEY_RESIDE_IN_NORTHERN_SAN_D_ORIA_PORT                                = 12763,  -- They reside in Northern San d'Oria, Port Bastok, and Port Windurst. To which thou yede is of no matter, as their message shall be the same.
        WHETHER_OR_NOT_THOU_UNDERTAKEST_THIS_EFFORTLESS_SWINK                  = 12764,  -- Whether or not thou undertakest this effortless swink to free thyself from thy shackles is a choice which is wholly thine to make.
        SLIP_THAT_UPON_THY_FINGER_AND_LET_THYSELF                              = 12765,  -- Slip that % upon thy finger and let thyself bathe in its luminescent emanations.
        VAGUE_IMAGES_OF_WORLDS_BEYOND_COALESCE_AND_DIFFUSE                     = 12766,  -- Vague images of worlds beyond coalesce and diffuse within.
        ENTER_THE_LIGHT_TAKE_ME_NOW_ABSOLUTELY_NOT                             = 12767,  -- Enter the light? Take me now! Absolutely not!
        ENTER_THE_LIGHT_TAKE_ME_NOW_I_LL                                       = 12768,  -- Enter the light? Take me now! I'll dive in head first! Absolutely not!
        NOTHING_HAPPENS_3                                                      = 12769,  -- Nothing happens...
        QUOTHA_THE_LIGHT_THAT_SHINES_FORTH_FROM_THY                            = 12770,  -- Quotha...the light that shines forth from thy soul hath brightened a considerable degree.
        NATHELESS_IT_REMAINETH_BUT_A_DULL_GLOW_AKIN                            = 12771,  -- Natheless, it remaineth but a dull glow akin to twitherym dust whenas compared to the blindingly refulgent souls of more accomplished combatants.
        TO_FULFIL_THY_TRUE_POTENTIAL_THOU_NEEDS_ASSUME                         = 12772,  -- To fulfil thy true potential, thou needs assume the role of gladiator and bathe in monipulator blood.
        AS_A_MONIPULATOR_THOU_HAST_LIKELY_REDUCED_OPPONENTS                    = 12773,  -- As a monipulator, thou hast likely reduced opponents everywhere to bawling babes at the mere mention of thy name.
        SIMULTANEOUSLY_THOUGH_COMBATANTS_WHO_HATH_CUT_SWATHS_THROUGH           = 12774,  -- Simultaneously, though, combatants who hath cut swaths through adversaries while inside bestial vessels betimes yearneth for more...to bite the hand that feedeth.
        A_SAGA_SUNG_OF_THOSE_WHO_INSTILL_TERROR                                = 12775,  -- A saga sung of those who instill terror and those who release the land from it... Bwahaha, a worthy tale of spiritual strife, forsooth.
        NOW_THAT_THE_STAGE_HATH_BEEN_SET_I                                     = 12776,  -- Now that the stage hath been set, I shall impart the extent of my gladiatorial knowledge to thee. Simply ask and thou shalt receive.
        WHAT_SHALL_YOU_ASK_ABOUT_BELLIGERENCY_RANKS_PRESTIGE                   = 12777,  -- What shall you ask about? Belligerency. Ranks. Prestige. Spoils. Domination. Nothing.
        THOSE_WHO_HAVE_THE_AMBITION_TO_SLAY_MONIPULATORS                       = 12778,  -- Those who have the ambition to slay monipulators can do battle against them by speaking with [me/my Northern San d'Orian ally] or one of my brethren in either [Port Bastok or Port Windurst/Northern San d'Oria or Port Windurst/Northern San d'Oria or Port Bastok] and receiving %.
        THIS_IS_THY_METAPHORICAL_MUSTER_AS_WELL_AS                             = 12779,  -- This % is thy metaphorical muster as well as official avowal to enter belligerency.
        WHILE_IT_DOTH_PROVIDE_MYRIAD_BOONS_TO_THEE                             = 12780,  -- While it doth provide myriad boons to thee, it preventeth not those outside thy coterie from interfering with thy duty. Such a benediction will only descend upon the yare souls who hath claimed monipulators as their prey.
        I_MUST_ALSO_CAUTION_THEE_TO_BEWARE_THAT                                = 12781,  -- I must also caution thee to beware that, depending on thy level of expertise, it may not behoove thee to tread upon the soils of certain lands.
        LASTLY_SHOULD_THY_BLOODLUST_CEASE_OR_RESOLVE_WITHER                    = 12782,  -- Lastly, should thy bloodlust cease or resolve wither on the vine, speak to me and I shall grant thee permission to withdraw from belligerency.
        LASTLY_SHOULD_THY_BLOODLUST_CEASE_OR_RESOLVE_WITHER_2                  = 12783,  -- Lastly, should thy bloodlust cease or resolve wither on the vine, speak to one of my compatriots and they shall grant thee permission to withdraw from belligerency.
        THREE_RANKS_DOTH_SERVE_TO_CLASSIFY_THE_WORLD                           = 12784,  -- Three ranks doth serve to classify the world's monipulator executioners. There is the eponymous gladiator (Gla), champion gladiator (CG), and high champion gladiator (HCG).
        NAUGHT_ELSE_NEEDS_BE_EXPLAINED_ANENT_THIS_SIMPLE                       = 12785,  -- Naught else needs be explained anent this simple concept...save that a gladiator's rank is determined by his prestige.
        PRESTIGE_IS_THE_GLADIATOR_S_EQUIVALENT_OF_THE                          = 12786,  -- Prestige is the gladiator's equivalent of the common adventurer's fame.
        DEFEATING_BOTH_MONSTERS_AND_MONIPULATORS_INCREASETH_THY_PRESTIGE       = 12787,  -- Defeating both monsters and monipulators increaseth thy prestige, while falling victim to their claws decreaseth it.
        EACH_RANK_ALSO_HATH_A_CORRESPONDING_MAXIMUM_AMOUNT                     = 12788,  -- Each rank also hath a corresponding maximum amount of prestige, much like the infamy of monipulators.
        ASCERTAINING_THY_CURRENT_PRESTIGE_IS_MERELY_A_TRIFLE                   = 12789,  -- Ascertaining thy current prestige is merely a trifle. (Access the Profile menu under Status.)
        OF_COURSE_PRESTIGE_IS_NOT_SIMPLY_A_MEANS                               = 12790,  -- Of course, prestige is not simply a means by which to boast to thy inferiors. Thou canst cede it to me in exchange for troves of splendid rewards.
        NO_VICTORY_DOTH_TASTE_AS_SWEET_AS_ONE                                  = 12791,  -- No victory doth taste as sweet as one where the stakes are high. Flaying treacherous notorious monsters and high notorious monsters occasionally earns thee spoils of war.
        A_LITTLE_COCKATRICE_TOLD_ME_THAT_MONIPULATORS_EVEN                     = 12792,  -- A little cockatrice told me that monipulators even relinquish equipment betimes, so hold not back from slicing, stabbing, and spellcasting thy savage enemies to smithereens.
        EKE_THE_EQUIPMENT_THOU_DOST_OBTAIN_MAY_BE                              = 12793,  -- Eke, the equipment thou dost obtain may be engraved with arcane glyptics.
        EKE_THE_EQUIPMENT_THOU_DOST_OBTAIN_MAY_BE_2                            = 12794,  -- Eke, the equipment thou dost obtain may be engraved with arcane glyptics by my consorts.
        ATHWART_TERRESTRIAL_BEINGS_SUCH_AS_THEE_OUR_MEZZOTINTING               = 12795,  -- Athwart terrestrial beings such as thee, our mezzotinting process leaveth nary a scratch on extant arcane glyptics.
        IN_SOOTH_IT_WOULD_BE_PURE_IDIOCY_TO                                    = 12796,  -- In sooth, it would be pure idiocy to charge nothing for our services. However, I shan't discuss figures at this juncture.
